it would help with debugging (when initially looking into logs) if the message contained the word "timeout", which is apparently the immediate reason of this message. E.g.: `"Attempt to authenticate with the salt master failed with timeout"`. At first sight, I thought this is something related to PKI infrastructure, authentication, etc, but it showed up to be just a lost network connection...
